Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:11.26,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.46,0:00:15.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground with a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:23.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.02,0:00:27.04,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning with a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:30.77,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.77,0:00:34.47,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.47,0:00:38.04,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,0:00:45.47,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Tearing through the\Nair with a Rider Plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.47,0:00:52.92,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great flight that\Nskates over the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.92,0:00:56.78,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up tornadoes with a Rider Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:01:00.79,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.79,0:01:04.29,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:08.29,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:11.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the Kamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.08,0:01:15.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.15,0:01:19.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.94,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx90\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,170.389)}The Terrifying Operation: Pet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.94,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs175\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(467.167,730.389)}Send Rider to Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.29,0:01:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this great?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.22,0:01:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I never knew air could taste so fresh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.90,0:01:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the best thing in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.45,0:01:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I hear a canary singing somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.49,0:01:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there canaries in this area?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.41,0:01:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.80,0:01:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Leave this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.58,0:02:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He's quite a little cutie, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.18,0:02:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not afraid of you, Mr. Yamanaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.51,0:02:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite appearances,\NI'm a kind and gentle man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Cute, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take it back and keep it as a pet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But its singing seems so strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.14,0:02:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.72,0:02:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoko, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.34,0:02:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... what's wrong with you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.06,0:03:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.80,0:03:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what happens when\Na snake hunts a frog?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.64,0:03:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're the frogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.04,0:03:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If I may.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.98,0:03:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.78,0:04:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What an awful way to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the cause of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Poisoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like they were bitten\Nby a venomous snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A venomous snake?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Four people were killed at the Tama River?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.25,0:04:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The police say they were\Nbitten by a venomous snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But you wouldn't see snakes around now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.59,0:04:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look! A canary!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.58,0:04:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.20,0:04:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.12,0:04:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.26,0:05:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's strangely tame...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You think it's someone's pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.92,0:05:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Small animals like me, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.38,0:05:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it really is tame!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.15,0:05:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The way it sings seems strange, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.90,0:05:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I found something we can use.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.80,0:05:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.02,0:05:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still usable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are, your own castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we feed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.90,0:05:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see. Canaries eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Normal bird food is fine, it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.61,0:05:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go buy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we have money?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what should we call it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.46,0:05:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Good question!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys, you've got work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.24,0:05:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:06:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Venomous snakes out of\Nseason, and a lost canary...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That looked like...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.22,0:06:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.84,0:06:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.06,0:06:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to use you to\Nlure out Hongo Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.44,0:06:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Come along!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.21,0:06:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a police car!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.49,0:07:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Help, Mr. Policeman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Policeman! Arrest Gel Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.70,0:07:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker... Do they look like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They're Gel Shocker, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I might find\Nsomething like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.24,0:07:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoki, Mitsuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi! Please, help!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.33,0:07:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He bit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's your chance! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I'm around,\Nyou won't have your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.94,0:08:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to tell Captain Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.68,0:08:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My head is pounding...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It... It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.22,0:08:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't stand it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambulance... call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:08:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hongo is fighting Gel Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.04,0:09:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.32,0:09:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,My head... it hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.91,0:09:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.43,0:09:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.07,0:09:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Mitsuru?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.82,0:09:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a grip!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.36,0:09:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.80,0:09:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... it's a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.37,0:09:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You see the power of Canarycobra?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's not even my strongest weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a bite from my cobra\Nhand's venomous fangs!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a Gel Shocker cyborg?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.32,0:10:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping you'd show, Hongo Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.57,0:10:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Witness the terrible\Nweapons of Canarycobra!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.87,0:10:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're a canary monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.84,0:11:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.18,0:12:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.84,0:12:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see to it that you\Nnever fight again, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:33.42,Bumper Episode 70-98,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\c&HE4EBE4&\pos(320,534)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Mr. Hongo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.09,0:13:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it hurt bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He caught me off guard,\Nbut I'll be better soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.78,0:13:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you'd better take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a nice, long rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.24,0:13:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing you permanently disabled\Nwould be worse in the long run.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.94,0:13:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:13:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll finish off that monster my...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:13:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.58,0:14:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If for just one more minute more...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thirty seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.52,0:14:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If those headaches had kept up,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,they would have driven us mad or killed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My head still doesn't feel right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Our mistake was assuming it\Nwas a cute little canary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.15,0:14:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Who'd have thought it was actually\Nthe Gel Shocker cyborg Canarycobra?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's important not to\Nlose our love for our pets,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and affection for small animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.76,0:14:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.96,0:14:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.24,0:14:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If they send those awful\Ncanaries all over in Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone will go mad or die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster swore revenge on you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.33,0:14:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.94,0:14:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker is still obsessed\Nwith world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll surely mount a counterattack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:15:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And they'll use any manner of dirty tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.90,0:15:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's use TV and radio to tell\Npeople about those weird canaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:09.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We've just received an urgent bulletin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.44,0:15:12.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Attention, residents of Tokyo\Nand the surrounding prefectures.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.40,0:15:17.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If a canary arrives at your house,\Nplease contact the police at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.79,0:15:19.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The canaries are dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:22.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Although their colors are\Njust like a standard canary,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.06,0:15:29.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,they have a strange song that\Nalmost sounds artificial.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.26,0:15:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the canary they were\Ntalking about on the radio!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoo! Shoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.33,0:15:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Operation: Pet is a roaring success.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.30,0:16:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Canarycobra is swiftly\Nracking up accomplishments.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.71,0:16:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon, everyone in Tokyo will be driven mad,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.59,0:16:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,throwing the city into a panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokyo will soon be a Gel Shocker outpost.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And the next time they meet,\NCanarycobra will destroy Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, a canary!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, I see a canary!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Come grab it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the canary they were\Ntalking about on TV...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama! Why won't you catch it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.14,0:16:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.70,0:16:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.96,0:16:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Omura household\Nin Fujimachi 1-7-18.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.82,0:17:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the canaries they\Nmentioned on TV is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Taro's pigeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gel Shocker monster\Nwas seen at Taro's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.33,0:17:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't take it off yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's better already?\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.65,0:17:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,To deceive your enemies, you\Nmust first deceive your allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.49,0:18:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm too late?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo. But your leg...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.33,0:18:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I got your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.37,0:18:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Canarycobra...\NI won't let you have your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, get them to safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.46,0:18:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.66,0:18:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.54,0:19:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Think you can get away, Hongo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.84,0:19:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I defeat you, all of Tokyo\Nwill belong to Gel Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to die, Hongo Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.94,0:20:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider, face me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.14,0:20:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You want another broken arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't break it now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.78,0:20:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I've enhanced it with steel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so powerful...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:55.33,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.33,0:20:58.41,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.12,0:21:02.17,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.17,0:21:05.94,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:09.54,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.54,0:21:12.96,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.34,0:21:15.71,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.52,0:21:18.96,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:23.88,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:27.16,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.68,0:21:38.15,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:41.93,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies made of demons
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.93,0:21:45.40,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten our friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:48.98,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:52.69,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.69,0:21:56.59,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my scarf of red...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.59,0:21:59.49,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.03,0:22:02.53,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.53,0:22:07.01,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.01,0:22:11.12,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.08,0:22:21.41,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.75,0:22:24.77,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies spreading fear
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.25,0:22:28.91,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten our towns,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.91,0:22:32.19,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.43,0:22:35.92,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.92,0:22:39.33,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my mask of green...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.66,0:22:42.76,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.31,0:22:46.11,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.90,0:22:50.42,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.42,0:22:53.67,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.29,0:20:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Nezcondor, and I'm\Nhere to send you to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.99,0:21:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.96,0:21:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Canarycobra.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.38,0:21:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's work together to kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.97,0:21:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.03,0:21:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can finish Rider off myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.91,0:21:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, it's your arm that will break!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.64,0:21:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it, Canarycobra!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.82,0:21:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right here, watching Rider die!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.58,0:22:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay, Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.72,0:22:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll handle the other one!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.54,0:22:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Lunar Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.08,0:22:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.06,0:22:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.83,0:22:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.12,0:22:59.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider defeated\Nthe terrifying Canarycobra,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.99,0:23:02.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,but a new monster, Nezcondor,\Nhas appeared in his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.94,0:23:07.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's used his terrifying power to\Nsend Taki Kazuya flying to his doom!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.07,0:23:10.84,Cont,,0,60,150,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.16,0:23:14.23,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs60\fnCalibri\pos(270.175,262.203)\c&HFFFFFF&}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.81,0:23:15.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A small fancy rat was fused with a condor
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.28,0:23:17.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,to be reborn as Nezcondor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.62,0:23:24.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Use your plague germs and razor-like\Nwings to destroy the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.26,0:23:25.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.32,0:23:31.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Let us meet again for phase\Ntwo of Operation: Pet, "Rider S.O.S!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.03,0:23:31.09,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs115\bord1\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,720.389)}The Terrifying Operation: Pet\NRider S.O.S!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.89,0:23:39.18,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,The wind gusts across the wasteland
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.18,0:23:42.62,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider traverses it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.62,0:23:46.72,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Alone, all alone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.72,0:23:49.97,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Holding back my sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.97,0:23:54.12,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,I fight, I fight alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.12,0:24:01.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Despite my solitude,\NI will do what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.02,0:24:06.46,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,to protect my friends and my home
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.46,0:24:12.64,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,I am the Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The Terrifying Operation: Pet\NSend Rider to Hell!